<br>
I had a GREAT group the other day in velks while collecting silks for the 5th shawl.  Me (51 wiz), 54 ench, 57(?) sk.<br>
We did awesome!  Chanter C2ed us all, and slowed mobs/hasted sk and pet.  SK tapped for healing, and I of couse nuked.  We killed very quickly and were never in danger of death really at all.  Nice exp too with the small group.<br>
<br>
Hraveob <p><img src="http://people.westminstercollege.edu/students/bdg0902/hraveob sig.jpg">
