<br>
Wizard<br>
Wizard<br>
Bard<br>
Ranger<br>
Rogue<br>
<br>
All level 60.  We'd assist the ranger pulling and would all cast while it was on the way in, would usually die in about 10 seconds.  I'd do a decent amount of the tanking with epic and bard songs would heal us up.  I was using Sunstrike and the other wizard had EER.  We were keeping the guardian, zone out and surrounding area clear.<br>
<br>
We eventually picked up a cleric, but she did more meleeing and casting than healing.<br>
